CustomField.description: AD-339 to see the In Year value for Contractual Products on an Opportunity
CustomField.formula: IF( AND( Annual_Contractual_Revenue__c <> 0, Annual_Contractual_GM__c <> 0 ), Annual_Contractual_GM__c / Annual_Contractual_Revenue__c, 0 )
CustomField.label: Annual Contractual GM%
